---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Projects" description="A collection of my projects and work.">
  <div class="space-y-8">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Projects</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-300">
        Here are some of the projects I've worked on. Each one represents a learning
        experience and an opportunity to solve interesting problems.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
      <!-- Project 1 -->
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#C99700]/20 bg-[#0C2340]/50 p-6 transition hover:border-[#C99700]/40">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">Wise Wizards Fitness</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-zinc-400">
          A fitness tracking application that helps users track and understand their fitness goals such as calorie counting and exercise tracking. This project combines my interests in health, data, and user-centered design to create a practical tool for fitness enthusiasts.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-500">
          Collaborated with Evan Bartek
        </p>
        <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            React
          </span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            JavaScript
          </span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            CSS
          </span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            HTML
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="text-[#C99700] hover:text-[#E5B84D] text-sm font-medium"
          >
            View Live →
          </a>
          <a
            href="#"
            class="text-[#C99700] hover:text-[#E5B84D] text-sm font-medium"
          >
            Source Code →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 2 -->
      <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#C99700]/20 bg-[#0C2340]/50 p-6 transition hover:border-[#C99700]/40">
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-2xl font-semibold">Campus Safety App Redesign</h2>
        <p class="mb-4 text-zinc-400">
          A collaborative project reimagining the University of Notre Dame's campus safety app to make it more user-friendly, reliable, and easy to access. This redesign focuses on improving the user experience and accessibility of critical safety information for students and faculty.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-zinc-500">
          Collaborated with class peers
        </p>
        <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            Figma
          </span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            UX Design
          </span>
          <span class="rounded-full bg-[#C99700]/20 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-[#C99700]">
            UI Design
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <a
            href="#"
            class="text-[#C99700] hover:text-[#E5B84D] text-sm font-medium"
          >
            View Design →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-lg border border-[#C99700]/20 bg-[#0C2340]/50 p-6 text-center">
      <p class="mb-4 text-zinc-300">
        Want to see more? Check out my GitHub for additional projects and contributions.
      </p>
      <a
        href="#"
        class="inline-block rounded-lg border border-[#C99700]/30 bg-[#0C2340]/50 px-6 py-3 font-medium text-[#C99700] transition hover:border-[#C99700]/50 hover:bg-[#0C2340]/70"
      >
        View on GitHub
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
